45, 108); cursor: pointer; border-top: none; border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 45, 108); border-left: none; border-image: initial; padding-bottom: 2px;">coronavirus pandemic</a>. The agency is continuing its review and has yet to issue a formal decision, the CDC told ABC News in a statement.</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 24px 0px; font-family: TiemposText, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28px; scroll-margin-top: 72px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">"We are finalizing our current assessment and will release more information later this week," the CDC said in a statement.</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 24px 0px; font-family: TiemposText, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28px; scroll-margin-top: 72px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The Associated Press&nbsp;<a href="https://abcnews.go.com/Politics/wireStory/ap-sources-broad-asylum-limits-border-end-23-83765336" target="_blank" style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; outline: 0px; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 45, 108); cursor: pointer; border-top: none; border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 45, 108); border-left: none; border-image: initial; padding-bottom: 2px;">was first to report</a>&nbsp;Title 42 would soon be rescinded.</p><p style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 24px 0px; font-family: TiemposText, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 28px; scroll-margin-top: 72px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">A court battle in which the administration faced a deadline to reimpose categorical expulsions of unaccompanied migrant minors or to ask an appellate court to